descriptionNullable:
![Images of Monarch and Viceroy butterflies from tiny dataset](https://github.com/KeithPinson/butterfly_mimics_2022_dataset/raw/main/DocResources/monarch_on_daisy-600.png)

[YOYMimics-2022-dataset.pdf](https://github.com/KeithPinson/butterfly_mimics_2022_dataset/blob/main/YOYMimics-2022-dataset.pdf)

This 2022 version of the dataset consists of 1028 total images. Each image is a 224x224 pixel jpg showing a single butterfly in the wild. The images are of 6 species of common North American butterflies. Some of the butterflies are toxic and some mimic the looks of the toxic. The images are for education and research purposes only. CSV files contain the labels and no label information is contained in the folder or image names. Additionally, a “tiny” dataset is included.

The abbreviated `tiny` dataset for image classification is of just 2 species with an accompanying
 [tiny dataset document](https://github.com/KeithPinson/butterfly_mimics_2022_dataset/blob/main/tiny/2022-Dataset-of-Butterfly-Mimics--Tiny.pdf).

![Images of Monarch and Viceroy butterflies from tiny dataset](https://github.com/KeithPinson/butterfly_mimics_2022_dataset/raw/main/DocResources/the-monarchs-and-viceroys.png)

The full `data` version the dataset for image classification is of 6 butterfly species. It too has an accompanying [dataset document](https://github.com/KeithPinson/butterfly_mimics_2022_dataset/blob/main/data/2022-Dataset-of-Butterfly-Mimics.pdf).

![Images of Black, Monarch, Pipevine, Spicebush, Tiger and Viceroy butterflies from the dataset](https://github.com/KeithPinson/butterfly_mimics_2022_dataset/raw/main/DocResources/the-butterflies.png)
title: 2022 Dataset of Butterfly Mimics
subtitle: Six Remarkable North American Butterflies
